                 "cityId" : "1"
             }

Post Mapping
http://localhost:8080/ticket :- allows user to book tickets

JSON Body :- {
                "auditoriumShowSeatIds" : [13,24,37],
                "userId" : "345"
             }

Post Mapping
http://localhost:8080/addAuditorium :- allows to add a auditorium to a theatre

